According to Physical Edge's website:

 The goal of Physical Edge is to be the physical therapy and fitness provider of choice for the greater Davis area.  This goal will be achieved by providing the highest quality of physical therapy and fitness services to the patients and clients that we serve.  We place the highest emphasis on customer service and providing a safe, pristine environment where everyone is made to feel comfortable.
